  01 Apr 2004; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org> snns-4.2-r3.ebuild:
  replacing patch by epatch

  17 Mar 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> snns-4.2-r4.ebuild:
